# Project Overview

This is a Next.js project template configured for deployment to Google Cloud Run. The project uses:

- [Next.js](mdc:https:/nextjs.org) 15.3.0 with App Router
- React 19
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS 4
- ESLint 9
- Docker for containerization
- Bun as a package manager (also supports pnpm)

## Key Files

- [package.json](mdc:package.json): Project dependencies and scripts
- [Dockerfile](mdc:Dockerfile): Multi-stage Docker build process
- [next.config.ts](mdc:next.config.ts): Next.js configuration
- [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json): TypeScript configuration
